01:40:34.501 --> 01:40:36.002
I thought better of you than that.

01:40:36.503 --> 01:40:36.968
You did?

01:40:37.003 --> 01:40:39.005
Well, wrong again.

01:40:39.506 --> 01:40:41.508
Listen, you've got all their
books and all their documents.

01:40:42.008 --> 01:40:44.010
Why do you need me who
knew practically nothing?

01:40:44.511 --> 01:40:47.013
