01:40:47.514 --> 01:40:48.765
Good-Bye, josh.

01:40:48.800 --> 01:40:50.016
Kennedy airport.

01:40:54.521 --> 01:40:56.488
Are you a bit of a cad,

01:40:56.523 --> 01:40:58.858
