01:42:13.099 --> 01:42:13.600
But they're not.

01:42:14.100 --> 01:42:15.101
There's a higher loyalty.

01:42:15.136 --> 01:42:16.603
The way I see it,

01:42:17.103 --> 01:42:19.439
Brutus was a good friend to Caesar.

01:42:20.607 --> 01:42:22.574
By stabbing him in the back,

01:42:22.609 --> 01:42:25.111
Brutus was a good friend to Caesar?

